<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Total URL Clicks</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .container a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .container .clicks {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .container .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Total URL Clicks</h1>
        <p>The number of clicks from the shortened URL that redirected the user to the destination page.</p>
        <hr>
        <p><b>Short URL : </b><a href="http://localhost:8001/url/<%= id %>">shortUrl.in/<%= id %></a></p>
        <div class="clicks"><%= click %></div>
        <form method="get" action="/test"><button class="button" type="submit">Shorten another URL</button></form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
